factor_title: Apramaycin sulfate, carbadox, and chlortetracycline hydroxchloride use
factor_description: All used as feed additives. Apramaycin sulfate: 150 g/ton as Apralan 7; 5 lb/pig at weaning. Carbadox: 50 g/ton as Mecadox 2.5; about 15 lb/pig. Chlortetracycline hydroxchloride: 250 g/ton; 14 days ad libitum.
group_exposed: Apramaycin sulfate, carbadox, and chlortetracycline hydroxchloride use
